Firmata 2.2 pure Java implementation

Licensed under Apache License 2.0

Forked by Stephan Muehlstrasser for using it under Android
https://github.com/smuehlst/Firmata

Build notes for Android with Eclipse:

Download slf4j-android-1.6.1-RC1.jar from http://www.slf4j.org/android/
and save it to the "lib" subdirectory

